{"tid":1879594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 澄清海關沒有阻礙口罩進口香港","createTime":"2020-02-14T09:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:23:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fc15ec9a39c3b415c1f18bdb39f942ee42645f13","tid":1879594,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"香港海關澄清有關口罩的失實傳言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  ​就近日不斷有傳言指，有從外地經空運郵遞寄運至香港的口罩於海關囤積，對市民收貨造成延誤，香港海關今日（二月十四日）再次嚴正澄清，有關傳言純屬捏造，並非事實。 <br />\n<br />\n  早前海關已就類似傳言於今年一月二十八日發放新聞稿予以澄清，惟近日仍有不少失實傳言聲稱海關阻礙口罩進口香港。香港海關認為有必要再次澄清，以正視聽。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人表示，海關於機場空郵中心的運作一直維持正常，亦安排充足人手及查驗設備進行清關工作。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人續說：「沒有到港貨物被海關積壓，空運郵遞及派送流程沒有被海關清關工作延誤。海關會繼續全力配合香港郵政於機場空郵中心處理到港郵件的流程。」<br />\n<br />\n  同時，海關會繼續根據風險評估和情報分析，按香港相關法例於各出入境管制站，對旅客、貨物、運輸工具及郵包進行清關／抽查工作，堵截違禁品及受管制物品非法進出香港。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月14日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間17時19分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/14/P2020021400529.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F14%2FP2020021400529.htm&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=c313e49c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/14/P2020021400529.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7b46f624e0b3edea940f681162f8300c10749891","tid":1879594,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"關於派口罩，我支持剩係派畀手足，歡迎入嚟屌柒我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1879264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1879264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e879d599d30f9513874ecfcd5b564a7cc84728e","tid":1879594,"uid":253016,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:40:34.000Z","msg":"即係有"},{"pid":"cb129131661a370a98a7c7566016a5a3789195d3","tid":1879594,"uid":33874,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n只係我同事係英國寄口罩返香港，係關口卡左一世姐<br />\n佢拆盒拆包裝再寄又順利入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62d4c29c2a80b07de8aac8f1f36db8037ceefd7","tid":1879594,"uid":3241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"即係有啦， 屌你卡關卡到呢"},{"pid":"e9ed76f34f37298013d5626bc5d9032def249786","tid":1879594,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"我信海關手腳好乾淨嘅，哩到係香港，你估大陸咩，有一國兩制架"},{"pid":"5e17fd6c78c48ab733d0a5793def4d7c605ac159","tid":1879594,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"撚有人信政府班狗閪咩"},{"pid":"f21a13e1292f6c416d59490f14ab5823d9d73ef9","tid":1879594,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"信政府一成， 而家咪要搶口罩貴貨囉<br />\n呢一刻仲信政府嘅垃圾死左都唔扺可憐"},{"pid":"2a2195a8245c54124edc5da64aa1b0dbdfdc2273","tid":1879594,"uid":166308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲冇阻 <br />\n係搶走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf5726a03533c6f2faaab63ed41087bba51eae4","tid":1879594,"uid":185045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"冇=有<br />\n有=做得比有的更過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f74fe7c8c5ba30a4135a91a6e42f84736bd441","tid":1879594,"uid":100337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ecf5726a03533c6f2faaab63ed41087bba51eae4","tid":1879594,"uid":185045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"冇=有<br />\n有=做得比有的更過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"同高登連登一樣<br />\n冇圖=冇圖<br />\n有圖=冇圖<br />\n多圖=得一張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8057b9dfe96b900ce695c6f35eb78f3838816286","tid":1879594,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14